# Cursor rules — IoT DevKit (Flutter)

唯一真理来源是项目根目录的 CLAUDE.md。请在动手前阅读并严格遵循它。

The single source of truth for this repo is CLAUDE.md in the project root.
Read it and follow it before making any changes — it covers commands, architecture,
state management / i18n / UI design-system rules, business boundaries, the test mapping,
and commit style. Do not duplicate those rules here.
